  "text": "On the other hand, early ionization of the IGM due to dissipation of fields can provide a substantial contribution to the optical depth to Thomson scattering [CITATION_1] . Requiring the additional contribution not to exceed ∆τ ∼ 0.1 (which seems compatible with the current limits from the CMB temperature and polarization power spectra), we find that the predicted y-type distortion is restricted to y 10 −8 .",
